node.text: Thank you so much to your service!

We need more South Asian professionals in MNC corporate jobs to volunteer and help bridge the language gaps. Pls also help your own citizens in Singapore.  They need you too!  Pls organize your community and help out in such trying times.

A/Prof. Zubair Amin is among the 800 medical staff from the National University Health System (NUHS) who are volunteering their time to provide on-site medical treatment in foreign worker dormitories. He shares his experiences and observations from his interactions with workers at Sungei Tengah Lodge.

Read more here: https://mothership.sg/…/zubair-amin-do…/
Prof Zubair Amin...salute to u Prof!🌸
This is our twins’ paediatrician at NUH! Prof Amin, so amazing that you are doing this, take care and hope to see you soon when you’re back to normal duty!
Thank you so much to your service!

We need more South Asian professionals in MNC corporate jobs to volunteer and help bridge the language gaps. Pls also help your own citizens in Singapore.  They need you too!  Pls organize your community and help out in such trying times.
